description:
With Colgate Pro Clinical Deep Clean Electric Power Toothbrush, experience a powerful yet gentle clean. The electric toothbrush has multi-directional vibrations, a 2 minute timer has 5 x plaque removal^, designed for your smile.

Designed for your smile, Colgate PRO Clinical Deep Clean Electric Toothbrush has 5x plaque removal^ and helps with healthier gums in 4 weeks*.

The Colgate ProClinical 250R Deep Clean Electric Toothbrush has multi-directional vibrations, with up to 30,000 strokes per minute. It has a slim, lightweight handle that is easy to control, a 2 minute timer with quadrant pacer and a rechargeable battery that lasts up to 10 days**.

Pack contents include:
- 1 x White Rechargeable toothbrush
- 2 x Deep clean replaceable brush heads
- 1 x Charger (AU plug)

Features of the deep clean replaceable brush head:
1. Compact head to clean back teeth
2. Soft thin-tipped bristles sweep along gum line
3. Power tip bristles clean hard-to-reach areas
4. Tongue and cheek cleaner helps remover odour causing bacteria

For optimal care, replace your brush head every 3 months and visit your dentist at least twice a year.

^vs a manual flat trim toothbrush.
*at the gum margin after 4 weeks vs a manual flat-trim toothbrush.
**when brushing twice daily.

ELECTRIC TOOTHBRUSH: Colgate PRO Clinical Deep Clean Electric Powered toothbrush has a rechargeable battery that lasts up to 10 days (when brushing twice daily), AU charger included.

5X PLAQUE REMOVAL: 250R PRO Clinical Electric Toothbrush has 5 x plaque removal vs a manual flat trim toothbrush

HEALTHIER GUMS IN 4 WEEKS: helps with healthier gums at the gum margin after 4 weeks vs a manual flat-trim toothbrush

2 MINUTE TIMER: Designed with a 2 minute timer and 30 second quadrant pacer to help with brushing habits

TONGUE CLEANER: Electric toothbrush head comes with a tongue and cheek cleaner to help remove odour causing bacteria
name: Colgate Proclinical 250r Deep Clean Sonic Electric Toothbrush 1 Pack
